(Lunarpine's already out of the CR chamber and carrying S. Wings body 
to a decent burial site.)

Lunarpine walked through the woods carrying the body of Shadow Wing, 
when Strikers voice came over the comm.

12592

Striker asked for a report.
Lunarpine heard Striker and chose to ignore him thinking "You missed 
the ark being beat on, unfortunately the Alliance didn't." 
The wolfbot reached the tree where Shadow Wing and him had thier 
first sparring match, where she'd caught him the first crow. he set 
down her body and transformed to wolf mode. moving his feet in a 
digging motion he began to dig a hole for her. He thought she'd 
approve of this gesture, in fact inside he could feel her aproval.
